<ul>
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>Jupyter Notebook</li>
    <li>Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Scikit-learn</li>
    <li>Power BI</li>
    <li>Machine Learning (Logistic Regression, Random Forest)</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>📈 Conclusion</h2>
<p>Through this project, I demonstrated a complete Data Science workflow:</p>
<ul>
    <li>From <strong>data cleaning and visualization</strong>,</li>
    <li>To <strong>machine learning model building</strong>,</li>
    <li>And delivering insights through an <strong>interactive dashboard</strong>.</li>
</ul>
<p>This project shows how data storytelling and predictive analytics can be combined to solve real-world problems.</p>

